        "field_name": "yAxisLabel",
        "reason": "由 raw form_data.y_axis_label 经 convertKeysToCamelCase() 生成。"
      },
      {
        "field_name": "yAxisBounds",
        "reason": "由 raw form_data.y_axis_bounds 经 convertKeysToCamelCase() 生成。"
      }
    ],
    "derived_query_fields": [
      {
        "field_name": "query.columns",
        "reason": "Bubble/buildQuery.ts 把 entity + series 组合后写到 query.columns。"
      },
      {
        "field_name": "query.metrics",
        "reason": "extractQueryFields.ts 会把 x / y / size 编译到 query.metrics。"
      },
      {
        "field_name": "query.orderby",
        "reason": "Bubble/buildQuery.ts 会把 root form_data.orderby 与 order_desc 重写成二维 orderby 数组。"
      }
    ],
    "runtime_derived_fields": [
      {
        "field_name": "echartOptions",
        "reason": "transformProps.ts 动态生成的 ECharts 配置，不是可保存的 form_data 字段。"
      },
      {
        "field_name": "refs",
        "reason": "transformProps.ts 为 tooltip / context menu 生成的运行时引用，不是 form_data 字段。"
      },
      {
        "field_name": "series",
        "reason": "transformProps.ts 里的本地变量名也叫 series，但那是 ECharts scatter series 数组，不要和 root form_data.series 维度字段混淆。"
      }
    ]
  },
  "api_usage_guidance": {
    "high_confidence_required_fields": [
      "datasource",
      "viz_type",
      "entity",
      "x",
      "y",
      "size"
    ],
    "recommended_always_set": [
      "adhoc_filters",
      "row_limit",
      "color_scheme",
      "show_legend",
      "legendType",
      "legendOrientation",
      "max_bubble_size",
      "tooltipSizeFormat",
      "opacity"
    ],
    "api_field_examples": [
      "entity",
      "series",
      "x",
      "y",
      "size",
      "orderby",
      "max_bubble_size",
      "tooltipSizeFormat",
      "xAxisBounds",
      "y_axis_bounds"
    ],
    "avoid_confusion": [
      "不要把正式 viz_type 写成旧测试值 echarts_bubble；Superset 6.0.0 正式值是 bubble_v2。",
      "不要把运行时别名 showLegend / maxBubbleSize / yAxisBounds 当成 API 主键；保存态 root form_data 仍应使用 show_legend / max_bubble_size / y_axis_bounds。",
      "不要把 Bubble/types.ts 里的 yAXisFormat 拼写错误照抄到模板。正式 API 主键是 y_axis_format。",
      "不要把 max_bubble_size 当成纯 number；当前 controlPanel choices 全是字符串。",
      "如果不需要对数轴，logXAxis / logYAxis 可以省略；源码默认值存在缺陷，显式写 false 也可以。"
    ]
  }
